    "biography": "<p>The Rust Monster resembles a giant armadillo with a long tail and two long front antennae. It’s attracted to the smell of metal, feeding on the rust it creates. When its antennae hit a target, any nonmagical metal armor or weapon crumbles to rust instantly. Magical metal items lose one 'plus' per hit unless they resist (10% chance per 'plus'—e.g., a shield +1 has a 10% chance to survive). The creature can be struck by any weapon type without harming the weapon if the body is hit, not the antennae.</p><p><strong>Terrain:</strong> Cavern, Ruins</p>",
